{"tid":1534120,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[原諒林鄭？]華人折中思維 會累死香港人","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T04:56:35.000Z","uid":25105,"like":79,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"08c1385d9df5f5ecd63dd2ebdc7c339012466d60","tid":1534120,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:02:48.000Z","msg":"魯迅：「中國人的性情是總喜歡調和折中的，譬如你說，這屋子太暗，須在這裏開一個窗，大家一定不允許的。但如果你主張拆掉屋頂他們就來調和，願意開窗了。」 <br />\n&mdash;&mdash;《無聲的中國》一九二七年<br />\n<br />\n一個作風強硬<br />\n二百萬人聲音唔聽<br />\n拘捕上千名政治犯既獨裁者<br />\n因為錄音流出佢去唔到salon <br />\n咁佢就係值得同情？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔可能</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我懷疑佢根本就係想一開始用超強硬作風<br />\n再用態度軟化<br />\n利用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">華人折中思維</span></strong></span>令疲憊既港人妥協<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好唔記得我地冇退路架<br />\n香港一輸就輸十年"},{"pid":"3e88cb30130bd0149ecd4863f630ed24eaa8755a","tid":1534120,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:03:13.000Z","msg":"一輸輸一年"},{"pid":"9aebec1a68b79c5cf2ce9fe8a5692c01654311c3","tid":1534120,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:03:23.000Z","msg":"兩年"},{"pid":"fb639a637c83535701cfe744f2b720def8a102f2","tid":1534120,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:03:33.000Z","msg":"三年"},{"pid":"11e639dd7536690a13291863ed4a309313f5f4b5","tid":1534120,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:03:43.000Z","msg":"四年"},{"pid":"c21923138fcfb7e3316d643173e94f214d130695","tid":1534120,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:03:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f696f2c5dfdcdad3de7a582ceb6229184482196b","tid":1534120,"uid":25105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:03:53.000Z","msg":"五年"},{"pid":"d92f3d2ebe4e66abc46beaed70ae4fcc2fd040c7","tid":1534120,"uid